My name is Matt Mills. I spit hot photos.

and then the blue note

Since it’s 6am, and I’m awake, I might as well blog these pictures. I lied, there’s one more post of drunk people, at Che’s birthday party. But they’re very well done drunk people.

Grammatical aside: does it annoy the hell out of anyone else when someone refers a blog post as just a ‘blog’? Blog isn’t just a post, it’s the collective noun for all those posts. Get it right, people.

And because I’m really bad about leaving tabs open and not hitting publish, it’s no longer 6am. At least my left arm is working right again. It was all weak earlier because someone slept on it wrong. Not sayin’ who, that’d be ungentlemanly.
